title: Wisdom from the Ninja Village of the Cold Moon by Stephen K Haye
description:
Wisdom from the Ninja Village of the Cold Moon
by Stephen K. Hayes. Contemporary Books, September 1984.

"Wisdom from the Ninja Village of the Cold Moon is an imaginative rendering of what could have been part of a scroll inspired by the epic saga of the Togakure ninja family."

This was hand-scanned into a PDF. The original is black and white except for red bars on the cover. Not every page is 100% perfectly aligned but since this has never been released in an electronic format and is getting rare (new copies go for over $100), I thought I would contribute an electronic version as best I can.
